message:
So my friend Jonathan Murphy from Chi Alpha has a message for you guys.

"For this coming year, I am looking to establish a Christian Student Union on campus that would function to 1) Bring unity to the on Christian community/ campus ministries and 2) Serve the Christian community and campus ministries. One Church will then become one of the methods or facets through which we bring unity. I am looking for 3-4 other mature Christian students who would be interested in being part of our leadership team. If you, or anyone you know has a heart and passion for our campus and Christian Unity, please PM or email me at murp0794@umn.edu, I would love to buy you a cup of coffee. 

If you have the ability and could share this message through any other ministry pages you are connected to (like Cru, Navs, A2F) it would be GREATLY appreciated!"

So if you guys are interested, let him know.
